{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LmVSPsj1p58v5Kt9kYZoVX","type":"tool_result","content":"File created successfully at: /Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Żurek Śląski.generated.22.txt"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7a96224f-17bb-4724-a834-ccff1a4d9776","uuid":"bcc71421-f587-420d-8031-b25b1d725107","tool_use_result":{"type":"create","filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Żurek Śląski.generated.22.txt","content":"Żurek Śląski\nSilesian Sour Rye Soup\n\nIngredients:\n- 2 lbs pork bones or knuckle meat\n- 4 cups water\n- 2 cups rye sourdough starter liquid (żur)\n- 1 large onion, quartered\n- 4 cloves garlic, minced\n- 3 carrots, sliced\n- 2 parsnips, sliced\n- 1 cup mushrooms, sliced\n- 3 bay leaves\n- 1 teaspoon caraway seeds\n- 1 teaspoon marjoram\n- 1/2 cup pearl barley (optional)\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- 2 hard-boiled eggs, halved\n- 1/4 cup fresh dill\n- Sour cream for serving\n- Rye bread for serving\n\nInstructions:\n\nStock preparation:\nBring water to boil in large pot.\nAdd pork bones and onion.\nSimmer 45 minutes, skimming foam.\nStrain stock, discard bones and onion.\n\nSoup:\nReturn stock to pot.\nAdd carrots, parsnips, mushrooms.\nAdd bay leaves, caraway seeds, marjoram.\nSimmer 20 minutes until vegetables are tender.\n\nAdd pork meat if using boneless cut, shred into bite-sized pieces.\nPour in żur liquid slowly, stirring constantly.\nAdd barley if using, simmer additional 20 minutes.\nSeason with salt and pepper to taste.\nAdjust sourness by adding more żur if desired.\n\nFinish:\nAdd fresh dill just before serving.\nPlace hard-boiled egg halves in bowl.\nLadle hot soup over eggs.\nTop with dollop of sour cream.\nServe with thick rye bread on the side.\n\nPrep time: 30 minutes\nCooking time: 90 minutes\nServes: 6-8 people\n\nNote: Żur (rye sourdough starter) can be made 3-5 days ahead\nby fermenting water with crushed rye bread at room temperature.","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
